name: Full user story test-case as generated user
description: Create new user, project, build configuration and run it as new user

steps.name: Create test user with fake user-data, generate fake project data

Sending POST request to http://localhost:8111/app/rest/users with data: {'username': 'Congress', 'password': 'Ql49BVg2qaA', 'email': 'alexawilson@example.com', 'roles': {'role': [{'roleId': 'PROJECT_ADMIN', 'scope': 'g'}]}}, expected_status: 200
Auth user with creds: "('Congress', 'Ql49BVg2qaA')" and get csrf token
Sending GET request to http://localhost:8111/authenticationTest.html?csrf with data: None, expected_status: 200
Send request to create new project

Sending POST request to http://localhost:8111/app/rest/projects with data: {'parentProject': {'locator': '_Root'}, 'name': 'present', 'id': 'UCywPdGHUQ8', 'copyAllAssociatedSettings': True}, expected_status: 200
Check if generated fake project ID: "UCywPdGHUQ8" equals ID from respond "UCywPdGHUQ8"
Create build conf for created project UCywPdGHUQ8

Create build configuration with data: {'id': 'wlBvSl2O0ir', 'name': 'tough', 'project': {'id': 'UCywPdGHUQ8'}, 'steps': {'name': 'outside', 'type': 'per', 'properties': {'property': [{'name': 'script.content', 'value': "echo 'Hello World!'"}, {'name': 'teamcity.step.mode', 'value': 'default'}, {'name': 'use.custom.script', 'value': 'true'}]}}}

Sending POST request to http://localhost:8111/app/rest/buildTypes with data: {'id': 'wlBvSl2O0ir', 'name': 'tough', 'project': {'id': 'UCywPdGHUQ8'}, 'steps': {'name': 'outside', 'type': 'per', 'properties': {'property': [{'name': 'script.content', 'value': "echo 'Hello World!'"}, {'name': 'teamcity.step.mode', 'value': 'default'}, {'name': 'use.custom.script', 'value': 'true'}]}}}, expected_status: 200
Check if created fake build conf ID: "wlBvSl2O0ir" equals ID from respond "wlBvSl2O0ir"
Test run created project build configuration with id: wlBvSl2O0ir
Sending POST request to http://localhost:8111/app/rest/buildQueue with data: {'buildType': {'id': 'wlBvSl2O0ir'}}, expected_status: 200
Verify that build with create fake id: "wlBvSl2O0ir" equals to build conf that was launched: "wlBvSl2O0ir"
